sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant C as Client
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant US as User Service
    participant OS as Order Service
    participant DB as Database

    C->>+GW: POST /api/orders (JWT)
    GW->>+Auth: Validate Token

    alt Token Valid
        Auth-->>-GW: 200 OK (user_id, roles)
        Note right of Auth: Token cached for 5 min

        GW->>+US: GET /users/{user_id}
        US->>+DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = ?
        DB-->>-US: User Record
        US-->>-GW: 200 User Profile

        GW->>+OS: POST /orders (user context)
        Note over GW,OS: Forwarded with X-User-Id header

        OS->>+DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
        OS->>DB: INSERT INTO orders (...)
        OS->>DB: UPDATE inventory SET qty = qty - 1
        DB-->>-OS: COMMIT OK

        OS->>+US: PATCH /users/{user_id}/stats
        Note right of US: Update order count
        US->>+DB: UPDATE user_stats SET total_orders = total_orders + 1
        DB-->>-US: 1 row updated
        US-->>-OS: 200 OK

        OS-->>-GW: 201 Created (order_id)
        GW-->>C: 201 Created

    else Token Expired
        Auth-->>GW: 401 Token Expired
        GW-->>C: 401 Unauthorized

    else Token Invalid
        Auth-->>GW: 403 Forbidden
        Note over Auth,GW: Log suspicious activity
        GW-->>C: 403 Forbidden
    end

    deactivate GW
